IDENTIFICATION DIVISION.
PROGRAM-ID. FIGURATIVE-HIGH-VALUES.

DATA DIVISION.
01 NUM-FIELD PICTURE IS 9(3).
01 TEXT-FIELD PICTURE IS X(3).
01 ALPHA-FIELD PICTURE IS A(3).
01 ZERO-FIELD PICTURE IS Z(3).
01 SIGNED-FIELD PICTURE IS S9(2).
01 DECIMAL-FIELD PICTURE IS 9V99.

PROCEDURE DIVISION.
MOVE HIGH-VALUES TO NUM-FIELD TEXT-FIELD ALPHA-FIELD ZERO-FIELD SIGNED-FIELD DECIMAL-FIELD.
